name: Set base path
Set 404
Create http endpoint <nodered>/files/xxx  where xxx is the file name to download
window redirect
format:
<script>
(function(scope) {
    scope.$watch('msg.payload', function(data) {
        if (data != undefined)
        {
            window.open("/files/"+ data +".json");
        }
        
    });
})(scope);
</script>
